text: Aleksandr Shkylev (, 1889 - 1914) was a Russian fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1889 births Category:1914 deaths Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
